participant_b.entity_text: serine/threonine kinase unc-51 like autophagy activating kinase 1

verbose_text: As reported, the serine/threonine kinase unc-51 like autophagy activating kinase 1 (ULK1), an upstream component of autophagy initiation, is phosphorylated and inhibited by mTOR.
